text: Joseph Moroni (born 10 January 1938) is a French rower. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics in Rome with the men's eight where they came fourth. ==References== Category:1938 births Category:Living people Category:French male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of France Category:Rowers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Seine-Saint-Denis Category:World Rowing Championships medalists for France Category:Rowers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:European Rowing Championships medalists
